body:
The report seems a side effect of opening the first transaction with hash `0x13314391098fca8c29fe07bb133504acd2db7ca2397399fef02efb6678a025c5`
Can be reproduced by opening the details panel when `wallet_fetchDecodedTxData` calls `eth_getBlockByNumber` which leads to this error. Following it it seems to be an issue/log from the Ethereum go lib while decoding the transaction data
@alaibe assigning you to this due to your recent work; maybe can quickly tell if this is fixable or a data issue with that specific transaction.
